name: Journey Home - Eighth Dream - Part 1
description: I have all my things neatly packed, she thought. Afterall that's why I have my briefcase. I just need to find my hat. I can't go anywhere without my hat. Where could I have left my hat? My hat doesn't go in the briefcase, that's why it's not in the briefcase, but it's still my thing, and I can't go anywhere if I don't have all my things. When I find my hat I'll make sure to put it in my briefcase.
